('a1559cfc-5370-4614-b9c0-31ff13660a8e', 1, 'summary', 'project', '{\"content\":\"The<span id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-99352e4e-7fff-ddbd-8607-95bcc725fd6a\\\"><ol style=\\\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;\\\"><li dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 19pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 18pt;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><h1 dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-right: 31.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\" role=\\\"presentation\\\" id=\\\"heading-0\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\\\">DOCUMENT</span></h1></li><ol style=\\\"padding-inline-start: 48px;\\\"><li dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 18pt; padding-left: 9pt;\\\" aria-level=\\\"2\\\"><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-right: 31.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\" role=\\\"presentation\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\\\">The creation of a document is based on a 2 level process per the example below:</span></p></li><li dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 18pt; padding-left: 9pt;\\\" aria-level=\\\"2\\\"><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-right: 31.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\" role=\\\"presentation\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\\\">Document1 (building block for rest of similar documents - “Templates”)</span></p></li><ol style=\\\"padding-inline-start: 48px;\\\"><li dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 4.5pt; padding-left: 4.5pt;\\\" aria-level=\\\"3\\\"><p dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-right: 31.5pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\\\" role=\\\"presentation\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 12pt; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\\\">The system is capable of having a content-locked feature after approval</span></p></li><li